This file will contain information about the project installation.

Install Java
============
Download and install java from http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javaee/downloads/index.html

Install Eclipse 
===============
Download and extract eclipse from http://eclipse.org/downloads/ 

Add following to eclipse.ini
-Xms512m
-Xmx1024m
-XX:+UseParallelGC
-XX:PermSize=256M
-XX:MaxPermSize=512M

Install Scala
=============
http://www.scala-lang.org/downloads

Install Git
===========
http://git-scm.com/

Software for Eclipse
====================
EGit
====
http://download.eclipse.org/egit/updates

Scala
=====
http://download.scala-ide.org/releases-29/2.0.0-beta

